430
00:33:06,500 --> 00:33:07,920
You’re the world to me.

431
00:33:08,420 --> 00:33:08,980
Tul.

432
00:33:24,580 --> 00:33:25,360
Hello, Can.

433
00:33:27,060 --> 00:33:27,700
Are you awake?

434
00:33:29,180 --> 00:33:30,020
I’m going to pick you up.

435
00:33:31,940 --> 00:33:32,800
