436
00:33:33,700 --> 00:33:34,780
Where are we going today?

437
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:35,740
Where do you want to go?

438
00:33:36,580 --> 00:33:37,720
I can take you anywhere you want.

439
00:33:38,520 --> 00:33:39,800
I want to go to your house.

440
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:42,000
I miss your chef’s cooking.

441
00:33:42,400 --> 00:33:44,600
Also, I want to do a movie marathon.

442
00:33:47,720 --> 00:33:49,280
