for my beloved mother.

493
00:36:21,320 --> 00:36:22,940
It's a lot.

494
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:31,360
Can he come to sleep over at my place tonight?

495
00:36:31,760 --> 00:36:32,440
Huh?

496
00:36:37,300 --> 00:36:38,260
About this.

497
00:36:38,500 --> 00:36:39,200
