507
00:37:02,020 --> 00:37:03,200
Good bye.

508
00:37:05,180 --> 00:37:06,860
Don’t make that grumpy face.

509
00:37:07,060 --> 00:37:07,660
Alright!

510
00:37:10,160 --> 00:37:13,600
